            "notes": "This deck aims to overwhelm opponents with a fast and aggressive strategy using Thrasios, Triton Hero and Ravos, Soultender as commanders. The deck includes a variety of mana dorks, tutors, and creature toolbox cards to efficiently ramp and tutor for key threats. The deck focuses on leveraging the partner abilities, such as recursion with Ravos and card advantage with Thrasios, to maintain pressure on the opponent. By utilizing a mix of disruption, removal spells, and powerful creatures, the deck aims to quickly assert board presence and out-tempo opponents. The partner combination of WUBG colors allows for access to a wide range of powerful spells, providing flexibility and resilience in various matchups."
